@r2_endorse_thalmann
title: 改投共产党的台尔曼。
subtitle: This will hurt our party's support.
view-if: spd_candidate != "Thälmann" and kpd_candidate = "Thälmann"
choose-if: kpd_relation >= 50 and left_strength > reformist_strength
unavailable-subtitle: [? if kpd_relation < 50 : We do not have good enough relations with the Communists, so they are not even willing to accept our support. ?] [? if reformist_strength >= left_strength : The reformist faction is able to dissuade the party from supporting this bizarre arrangement. ?]
on-arrival: reformist_dissent += 15; center_dissent += 10; labor_dissent += 5; neorevisionist_dissent += 10; catholics_spd -= 5; workers_spd -= 3; kpd_relation += 10; communist_coalition += 2; z_relation -= 15; dvp_relation -= 15; ddp_relation -= 12
on-departure: z_candidate = "Adenauer" if z_candidate = "Braun" or z_candidate = "Schumacher" or z_candidate = "Juchacz"; ddp_candidate = z_candidate if ddp_candidate = "Braun" or ddp_candidate = "Schumacher" or ddp_candidate = "Juchacz"; dvp_candidate = z_candidate if dvp_candidate = "Braun" or dvp_candidate = "Schumacher" or dvp_candidate = "Juchacz"; spd_candidate = "Thälmann";
max-visits: 1

我们将背书转向共产党的恩斯特·台尔曼。[? if z_candidate = spd_candidate : 原本盟友中央党视此举为背叛。 ?][? if z_candidate = "Braun" or z_candidate = "Schumacher" or z_candidate = "Juchacz": 他们现在将再次支持康拉德·阿登纳。 ?][? if ddp_candidate = "Braun" or ddp_candidate = "Schumacher" or ddp_candidate = "Juchacz": [+ ddp_name +] 也将转而支持中央党候选人。 ?][? if dvp_candidate = "Braun" or dvp_candidate = "Schumacher" or dvp_candidate = "Juchacz": DVP亦将支持中央党候选人。 ?]

- @r2_vote: 投票开始。

@r2_endorse_munzenberg
title: 改投共产党的明岑伯格。
subtitle: This will hurt our party's support.
view-if: spd_candidate != "Münzenberg" and kpd_candidate = "Münzenberg"
choose-if: kpd_relation >= 50 and left_strength > reformist_strength
unavailable-subtitle: [? if kpd_relation < 50 : We do not have good enough relations with the Communists, so they are not even willing to accept our support. ?] [? if reformist_strength >= left_strength : The reformist faction is able to dissuade the party from supporting this bizarre arrangement. ?]
on-arrival: reformist_dissent += 12; center_dissent += 10; labor_dissent += 5; neorevisionist_dissent += 10; catholics_spd -= 5; workers_spd -= 3; kpd_relation += 10; communist_coalition += 2; z_relation -= 12; ddp_relation -= 10; dvp_relation -= 15;
on-departure: z_candidate = "Adenauer" if z_candidate = "Braun" or z_candidate = "Schumacher" or z_candidate = "Juchacz"; ddp_candidate = z_candidate if ddp_candidate = "Braun" or ddp_candidate = "Schumacher" or ddp_candidate = "Juchacz"; dvp_candidate = z_candidate if dvp_candidate = "Braun" or dvp_candidate = "Schumacher" or dvp_candidate = "Juchacz"; spd_candidate = "Münzenberg";
max-visits: 1

我们将背书转向共产党的维利·明岑伯格。[? if z_candidate = spd_candidate : 原本盟友中央党视此举为背叛。 ?][? if z_candidate = "Braun" or z_candidate = "Schumacher" or z_candidate = "Juchacz": 他们现在将再次支持康拉德·阿登纳。 ?][? if ddp_candidate = "Braun" or ddp_candidate = "Schumacher" or ddp_candidate = "Juchacz": [+ ddp_name +] 也将转而支持中央党候选人。 ?][? if dvp_candidate = "Braun" or dvp_candidate = "Schumacher" or dvp_candidate = "Juchacz": DVP亦将支持中央党候选人。 ?]

- @r2_vote: 投票开始。


@r2_endorse_adenauer
title: 改投中央党的康拉德·阿登纳。
view-if: z_candidate = "Adenauer" and spd_candidate != z_candidate
on-departure: kpd_candidate = "Thälmann" if kpd_candidate == spd_candidate and kpd_party_leader != "Conciliators"; kpd_candidate = "Münzenberg" if kpd_candidate == spd_candidate and kpd_party_leader == "Conciliators"; sapd_candidate = kpd_candidate; spd_candidate = "Adenauer"; z_relation += 4; Adenauer_bonus -= 2.5 if z_relation < 40; Seldte_bonus += 2.5 if z_relation < 40; is_unity_candidate = 1
go-to: r2_campaigning

