[? if dvp_relation < 40 : 在我党支持盖斯勒之后，DVP内原本支持他的部分与之分道扬镳，转而支持塞尔德特。 ?]

[? if kpd_candidate = spd_candidate: 共产党现在与我党此前的联盟决裂，转而支持本党候选人。 ?]



@r2_endorse_eckener
title: 说服魏玛联合各党共同支持雨果·埃克纳。
subtitle: -2 resources
unavailable-subtitle: [? if resources < 2 : -2 resources - Not enough resources. ?]
choose-if: resources >= 2 and ((z_relation >= 50 and z_leader = "Kaas") or (z_relation >= 30 and z_leader = "Joos")) and ddp_relation >= 40
view-if: z_candidate = "Adenauer" and ddp_candidate = "Gessler" and spd_candidate != "Eckener"
on-arrival: kpd_candidate = "Thälmann" if kpd_candidate == spd_candidate and kpd_party_leader != "Conciliators"; kpd_candidate = "Münzenberg" if kpd_candidate == spd_candidate and kpd_party_leader == "Conciliators"; sapd_candidate = kpd_candidate; spd_candidate = "Eckener"; z_candidate = "Eckener"; ddp_candidate = "Eckener"; resources -= 2; is_unity_candidate = 1
go-to: r2_campaigning

我们已成功使魏玛联合各党在雨果·埃克纳之下团结起来！



