@hitler_victory
on-arrival: chancellor = "Hitler"; chancellor_party = "NSDAP"; hitler_seen = 0

随着 [+ nsdap_candidate +] 的胜利，纳粹党马不停蹄地巩固权力。[? if president = "Göring": 他的首项举措便是罢免现任总理，并任命希特勒为总理——首先撤销了对希特勒的驱逐令。 ?][? if president = "Hitler": 他的首项举措便是罢免现任总理，自任总理，并以冲锋队袭击一切反对者。 ?]

- @hitler_takes_power: 接下来呢？
- @hitler_constitutional: 这违反宪法！

@seldte_victory
on-arrival: chancellor = "Hitler"; chancellor_party = "NSDAP"; hitler_seen = 0

随着塞尔德特的胜利，权力天平倒向纳粹党。[? if hitler_deported: 他的首项举措便是罢免现任总理，任命阿道夫·希特勒为总理——首先撤销了对希特勒的驱逐令。 ?][? if not hitler_deported: 他的首项举措便是罢免现任总理，任命阿道夫·希特勒为总理。 ?]

- @hitler_takes_power: 接下来呢？
- @hitler_constitutional: 这赤裸裸地违反宪法！

@hitler_constitutional
view-if: presidential_powers

我们已通过宪法修正案，剥夺了总统任意罢免政府的权力。为撤销此条款，极右翼发起了新宪法修正案的公投。冲锋队走上街头，「劝说」选民支持其提案。德国濒临内战。

- @fight: 我们要上街与法西斯战斗！
- @defeat_democratic: 我们只能通过民主途径战胜法西斯！

@fight

我们清楚这意味着内战、对抗整个国家机器吗？

- @civil_war: 是的。
- @defeat_democratic: 通过宪法手段反击为时未晚。

@defeat_democratic
on-arrival: {!
Q.pro_democracy_votes = Q.spd_votes + Q.ddp_votes + Q.z_votes - (Q.sa_strength*Q.sa_militancy/10) + (Q.rb_strength*Q.rb_militancy/10);
if (Q.pro_republic >= 60) {
    Q.pro_democracy_votes += Q.kpd_votes;
    Q.pro_democracy_votes += Q.dvp_votes;
}
!}
go-to: ref_win if pro_democracy_votes >= 50; ref_lose if pro_democracy_votes < 50

@ref_win
on-arrival: constitutional_crisis = 1

尽管纳粹党威胁不断，社民党与各民主政党的支持者们仍拒绝出席公投，致使其得票率达不到通过门槛。这是一场小小的胜利——冲锋队仍在街头横行无忌。通往绝对权力的合宪之路已封闭，但这能阻止纳粹党吗？

- @game_over: 结局尚不可知……

@ref_lose

- @hitler_takes_power: 接下来呢？


@election_end
go-to: eckener_win if winner = "Eckener"; juchacz_win if winner = "Juchacz"; bundesrepublik_win if winner = "Schumacher" or winner = "Adenauer"; hitler_victory if winner = "Hitler" or winner = "Göring" or winner = "Goring"; seldte_victory if winner = "Seldte"; munzenberg_victory if winner = "Munzenberg" or winner = "Münzenberg"; thalmann_victory if winner = "Thalmann" or winner = "Thälmann"; nazis_lose if winner = "Braun" or winner = "Gessler"; cultural_victory if winner = "Ossietzky" or winner = "Mann"; einstein_victory if winner = "Einstein"
on-arrival: president = winner; president = "Thälmann" if president == "Thalmann"; president = "Münzenberg" if president = "Munzenberg"; president = "Göring" if president = "Goring"

选举已由 [+ winner_desc +] 获胜。

@thalmann_victory
go-to: thalmann_democrat if presidential_powers; thalmann_civil_war if not presidential_powers

@thalmann_civil_war
on-arrival: kpd_relation = 80

# TODO: depose the chancellor?

台尔曼马不停蹄地巩固权力，动用一切手段重塑政府。极右翼随即发动政变。我们别无选择，只能与共产党联合对抗法西斯……

- @civil_war: 这就是内战。

@thalmann_democrat

虽然反宪政的台尔曼获胜，但他似乎正在遵守对总统权力的宪法约束——至少目前如此。右翼目前并无政变意愿。资产阶级只能与一位共产党总统共处——至少目前如此。


@munzenberg_victory
achievement: rote_millionar
go-to: nazis_lose

对于一位共产党总统的前景，资产阶级与右翼政党群情激昂；但明岑伯格与共产党调和派全力向德国保证他们对民主共和国的承诺。目前并无发动政变的动力。资产阶级只能接受新现实。

@eckener_win
achievement: zeppelin_kapitan
go-to: nazis_lose


@juchacz_win
