@nazis_lose
on-arrival: nazi_peak = 1; nazi_peak_timer = 2; nazi_peak_timer += (nsdap_votes/5); nazi_decline = 1; pro_republic += 10

选举失利之后，NSDAP-DNVP联盟陷入内讧与财务破产。极右翼的时刻似乎已暂告结束——至少目前如此。